                            <comment id="13203942" author="knutanders" created="Wed, 8 Feb 2012 20:23:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;To get the tests to run on Java 8, first run the following command:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;svn copy java/testing/org/apache/derbyTesting/functionTests/harness/jdk17.java java/testing/org/apache/derbyTesting/functionTests/harness/jdk18.java&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And then apply the attached jdk18.diff patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m running the full derbyall suite on Java 8 now to see if there are more things missing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13203992" author="knutanders" created="Wed, 8 Feb 2012 21:15:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Derbyall passed. Committed revision 1242098.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also plan to backport the fix to 10.8.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
